---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Redrock Strategic Advisors">
  <section
    class="relative h-screen overflow-hidden"
  >
    <img src="/RedrockCanyon.jpg" alt="Redrock Canyon" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />

    <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center h-full px-4">
      <div class="relative max-w-2xl w-full pt-8">
        <div class="hero-red-bar absolute left-0 md:left-6 z-10 inline-block px-6 py-4" style="background-color: #C80026; top: -10; transform: translateY(0);">
          <h1 class="text-white text-base md:text-2xl font-bold leading-tight">Your Partner for the Middle Market.</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8" style="background-color: rgba(220, 220, 220, 0.55); backdrop-filter: blur(2px); padding-top: 2rem;">
          <p class="text-base md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-secondary-900" style="padding: 1rem 2.5rem 1rem 3rem;">
            <b>Redrock Strategic Advisors</b> partners with middle-market business owners to achieve critical corporate milestones. Whether selling your business, transitioning ownership generationally, expanding through acquisitions, raising capital, or planning an exit, we deliver results that matter. 
		<br>
		<br>
		From first conversation to final closing—and beyond—we are your dedicated partner. 
		</br>
		</br> 
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service links at bottom of hero -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-10">
      <div class="container-wide flex items-center justify-center gap-2 py-6 text-white font-sans text-sm md:text-base font-medium tracking-wide text-center">
        <a href="/services/mergers-and-acquisitions" class="text-white hover:text-white no-underline hover:underline underline-offset-4">Mergers &amp; Acquisitions</a>
        <span class="text-white/60">|</span>
        <a href="/services/capital-advisory" class="text-white hover:text-white no-underline hover:underline underline-offset-4">Capital Advisory</a>
        <span class="text-white/60">|</span>
        <a href="/services/strategic-and-board-advisory" class="text-white hover:text-white no-underline hover:underline underline-offset-4">Strategic &amp; Board Advisory</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Focus section-->
  <section class="container-wide py-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <h2>Our Focus</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-2/3">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-secondary-800">

	Landscapes are shaped by massive tectonic shifts or constant flows to create grand canyons. <b>Markets and businesses</b> are similarly formed through massive innovations driving 	amazing opportunity, or through constant, recurring service and experiences that form bedrock customers that drive real value. <b>Redrock's professionals uniquely understand your 	business landscape and help navigate complex transactions and opportunities.</b>

	<br></br>
	
	Redrock Strategic Advisors helps middle-market business owners, boards and executive teams see new landscapes. Whether you're selling your business, acquiring a competitor or new 	capabilities, finding a capital solution, or planning your exit, we deliver results that matter. From first conversation to final closing—and beyond—we're your dedicated guide.

        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    </section>


  <!-- Our Approach section -->
  <section class="bg-secondary-50 py-20">
    <div class="container-wide flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-2/3">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-secondary-800 mb-6">
	We approach every opportunity to advise our clients as a partnership. We leverage decades of experience over 100+ transactions representing $5.5B+ of transaction value to develop a 	<b>custom approach</b> that addresses our clients' objectives. We focus on designing and managing every aspect of the transaction process to ensure measurable results, with an approach that encompasses:
	</p>
        <ul class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-secondary-800 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><b>Strategy.</b> Understanding our client's long-term strategy and market opportunity is critical to developing the right transaction process.</li>
          <li><b>Preparation.</b> We focus on upfront preparation to maintain momentum in the transaction once we engage the market.</li>
          <li><b>Execution.</b> Timeline-driven approach with the right information prepared to engage the right universe of counterparties, while maintaining competitive momentum to keep interest and attention through the closing of the intended transaction. </li>
          <li><b>Management Support.</b> Redrock functions as an extension of our client's management team, investors and board to support, coach and advise through unique transactions from start to completion and beyond.</li>
          <li><b>Advanced Resources.</b> Redrock's team relies on a constantly advancing set of databases, tools, technologies, and resources that support our team behind the scenes to streamline and improve the outcome of every project. </li>
          <li><b>Long-term Support.</b> With an emphasis on completing a transaction, our team remains engaged and available after the completion of a project. We are excited to continue to support our clients through multiple stages in a business's lifecycle.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Commitment section -->
  <section class="container-wide py-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-2/3">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-secondary-800">
          We are independent with a singular focus on understanding and executing <b><u>our clients'</u></b> merger, acquisition, capital solution, or strategic advisory assignment through to completion. We advise purposefully with our clients' objective in mind.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Career Path section -->
  <section class="bg-secondary-50 py-20">
    <div class="container-wide flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <h2>Let's Grow <b>Together</b></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-2/3">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-secondary-800 mb-6">
	Redrock is building a dedicated team of strategic advisors in a culture centered on <strong>client success and professional development</strong>. We believe this provides our team members with a path to a long-term career full of meaningful rewards, relationships and work. We promote from within and want to provide an opportunity for each team member to advance to become partners at Redrock Strategic Advisors.
	</p>
        <a href="/career-path" class="learn-more-btn">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


</BaseLayout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .hero-red-bar {
      left: 0 !important;
      right: 0;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  .learn-more-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1.5px solid #C80026;
    color: #C80026;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .learn-more-btn:hover {
    background-color: #C80026;
    color: white;
  }
</style>
